snippet.title: Metal Slug Tactics: 19 Minutes of Gameplay
snippet.description:
Enjoy this huge new chunk of gameplay from Metal Slug Tactics, the tactical RPG based in the Metal Slug universe. This footage shows off three characters along with their abilities: Clark Still, Ralf Jones, and Leona Heidern. Metal Slug Tactics will be released on November 5 for PC, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.

#MetalSlugTactics #Gameplay #RPG
